tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE parties_involved (
    party_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    case_id INT NOT NULL,
    party_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    party_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    FOREIGN KEY (case_id) REFERENCES intellectual_property_cases(case_id)
);

CREATE TABLE case_documents (
    document_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    case_id INT NOT NULL,
    document_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    document_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    document_url TEXT,
    FOREIGN KEY (case_id) REFERENCES intellectual_property_cases(case_id)
);

CREATE TABLE case_notes (
    note_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    case_id INT NOT NULL,
    note_content TEXT NOT NULL,
    created_at TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    FOREIGN KEY (case_id) REFERENCES intellectual_property_cases(case_id)
);

CREATE TABLE intellectual_property_cases (
  case_number INT PRIMARY KEY,
  plaintiff_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  defendant_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  case_details TEXT,
  resolution_status VARCHAR(20) CHECK (resolution_status IN ('pending', 'resolved'))
)

CREATE TABLE case_documents (
  document_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  case_number INT NOT NULL,
  document_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  document_content TEXT,
  FOREIGN KEY (case_number) REFERENCES intellectual_property_cases(case_number)
)

CREATE TABLE parties_involved (
  party_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  party_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  party_type VARCHAR(30) NOT NULL,
  party_role VARCHAR(30) NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE case_outcomes (
  outcome_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  case_number INT NOT NULL,
  outcome_description TEXT,
  resolution_date DATE,
  FOREIGN KEY (case_number) REFERENCES intellectual_property_cases(case_number)
)

CREATE TABLE legal_representatives (
  lawyer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  lawyer_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  firm_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  contact_details VARCHAR(100)
)
